{"tid":1954001,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚 隻眼生左粒唔知咩","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T13:19:59.000Z","uid":109010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5a2dddde62e3c45af655137cfeb84a70d797e4","tid":1954001,"uid":109010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"隻眼之前生左眼瘡<br />\n後來去左睇醫生 搽左d藥膏<br />\n搽左一排粒瘡爆左 但生左粒咁既野出後<br />\n想知係咩黎 已經生左一星期都未好 <br />\n類似張圖咁 不過唔係我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEdDEe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEdDEe8.png&h=72a9fa26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98c4623e3ffe83b860090a784532b67c49a4f60e","tid":1954001,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"試下每日熱敷，有可能係油脂粒"},{"pid":"ea47af9e0ee2603e6880fcf2a5f4af235f585879","tid":1954001,"uid":177878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生好啲，驚係腫瘤"},{"pid":"e514503f4b36234db4f6c5a7bab511ff09a0c1d4","tid":1954001,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"下世再見"},{"pid":"fb43e4e9913a88551316838a567a848af586e5bd","tid":1954001,"uid":244369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"要外科醫生, 好簡單切左佢。"},{"pid":"f7f63c7f212bfbcad13ae8d7fa23f0c8b2855620","tid":1954001,"uid":285405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"試下去公立診所睇下咩黎好，以前試過生眼瘡，唔癢唔痛，一直無理好礙眼。<br />\n<br />\n之後公立診所幫我睇完就排期半年，去醫院幫我做小手術切除左就無事。個小手術會打麻醉針落眼皮位置之後醫生用d野整爆佢，一陣間就整完，即時走得。"}]}